rows.label: qst103409_msg0002
rows.name: Akatsuki and his Driver? Is that true?

rows.label: qst103409_msg0003
rows.name: The Core Crystal... Is it Akatsuki's?

rows.label: qst103409_msg0004
rows.name:
May I take this into my
custody as evidence?

rows.label: qst103409_msg0006
rows.name:
With this, the anti-imperialist
organization Brionac is
all but destroyed.

rows.label: qst103409_msg0007
rows.name:
What did you say?
Another organization?!

rows.label: qst103409_msg0008
rows.name:
Lindwurm... I have never
heard such a name.

rows.label: qst103409_msg0009
rows.name:
What Akatsuki said is not
necessarily the truth.

rows.label: qst103409_msg0010
rows.name:
He has taunted you and let you
escape before, after all.

rows.label: qst103409_msg0011
rows.name:
...Thank you for your
service to the Empire.

rows.label: qst103409_msg0012
rows.name:
We will handle the cleanup
of the remaining small fry,
so please do not worry.
